data.description: Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac sits this popular LaSalle floorplan offering 2 bedrooms plus an office and 2 bathrooms. Backing to a beautiful park-like greenspace, it provides lots of privacy with no neighbors behind. Overlook and enjoy the tranquility of nature through the large picture window installed by the current owners. Tile and wood floors throughout makes this home easy to clean and maintain. Added cabinets in the utility room offer additional storage. This property also boasts a sun room with a built-in desk area that can be easily converted to a crafting station or dry bar or whatever your imagination can create. Retractable awning offers shade from the mid-day sun. The kitchen includes granite countertops while the island stands out with beautifully marbled granite. Completing the kitchen area is a breakfast bar, eat-in breakfast area, built-in electric cooktop, oven and microwave. Open to the living area, the cook is not separated from all the fun. Added bonus, primary bedroom is on one side of the home and the guest bedroom is on the other offering complete privacy for owner and visitors. All the space  you need with privacy and tranquility!
